abstract: A dictionary of custom properties to use with the URL template.
overview:
## Discussion

The `data` object holds a dictionary of custom properties to fill the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/TileOverlay/urlTemplate].

The default value is `{}`.

This example shows adding a customized tile overlay to a map.

items.description: A string, or callback function that returns a string, with a URL that provides the requested tile.
items.name: urlTemplate

items.description: Reloads the tile overlay for the displayed map region with the latest data values.
items.name: reload()
